Readme
------
This module includes some utilities related to ezmlm.  For now, it only has a box and a form for subscribing for ezmlm lists.


Feel free to add other functionnalities in there!

Author: steph@alternatives.ca

Requirements
------------

This module requires Drupal 4.2 or later.

Installation
------------

1. Copy the chatbox.module to the Drupal modules/ directory. Drupal should
   automatically detect it.

2. Go to the configuration menu and configure the ezmlm module  

   


Author
